short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Gives you ability to change the final score at https://kwalifikacjewzawodzie.pl/

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
After you finished the exam at kwalifikacjewzawodzie.pl, you can edit the final score.
You do that by clicking at "https://kwalifikacjewzawodzie.pl//" on the bottom left of the site, the window prompt will appear for you to enter the desired score. Extension will also automatically calculate the percentage of your total score.
